---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About CodeToCash — Marketing Education for Developers"
  description="CodeToCash teaches vibe coders and indie developers how to sell their products using direct response marketing. Learn the frameworks, tools, and tactics."
>

  <!-- ============ HERO SECTION ============ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden px-4 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <!-- Background glow -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[400px] bg-coral/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-pulse-slow"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="inline-block text-sm font-mono text-coral uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 animate-fade-in">// about us</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-tight animate-fade-in-up">
        About <span class="text-coral">CodeToCash</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-200">
        We help vibe coders and indie developers learn the one skill school never taught: how to sell what you build.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ============ THE STORY SECTION ============ -->
  <section class="relative px-4 py-24 sm:py-32 bg-navy-light/50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 section-animate">
        <p class="text-sm font-mono text-coral uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">// the story</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
          Why CodeToCash Exists
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 section-animate">
        <!-- The Problem -->
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" /><path d="M12 8v4M12 16h.01" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.06] mt-3"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Problem</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Thousands of talented developers build incredible products every day with Cursor, Bolt, Lovable, Replit — tools that make shipping faster than ever. But most of those products never earn a dollar. Not because the code is bad or the idea is wrong, but because nobody taught these developers how to put their work in front of the right people and convince them to buy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The Gap -->
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.06] mt-3"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Gap</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Traditional marketing education is designed for MBA students and marketing agencies. It's full of vague brand strategy, abstract positioning frameworks, and case studies about Fortune 500 companies. It doesn't speak developer. It doesn't think in systems. It doesn't ship fast. And it definitely doesn't help a solo dev figure out why their SaaS landing page has a 0.2% conversion rate.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The Solution -->
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.06] mt-3"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Solution</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              CodeToCash was built to bridge that gap. We take the most powerful marketing framework ever created — direct response marketing — and translate it for the people who build the future: developers. DRM is systematic, measurable, and iterative. It's marketing that thinks like code. You write a headline like you'd write a function: with a clear input, a clear output, and a way to test if it works.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The Mission -->
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14" /><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4" /></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Our mission is simple: <span class="text-white font-medium">help 10,000 developers earn their first $1,000 from something they built.</span> Not from freelancing. Not from a job. From their own product, sold to real customers, using marketing that actually works. If you've ever shipped something you're proud of and wondered why nobody bought it, this is for you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ============ WHAT WE BELIEVE SECTION ============ -->
  <section class="relative px-4 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 section-animate">
        <p class="text-sm font-mono text-coral uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">// our values</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
          What We Believe
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Belief 1 -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all duration-300 section-animate">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">"Marketing is a skill, not a talent"</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-mono text-coral mb-4">// learnable</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Anyone can learn it. Especially developers who already think in systems, logic, and iteration. You don't need to be "creative" or "extroverted." You need frameworks, and you need to practice.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Belief 2 -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all duration-300 section-animate">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">"Test everything, assume nothing"</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-mono text-coral mb-4">// data-driven</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            DRM is the scientific method applied to selling. We don't believe in "best practices" that haven't been measured. We believe in hypotheses, experiments, and data. Opinions are cheap. Conversion rates are truth.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Belief 3 -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all duration-300 section-animate">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">"Ship first, optimize later"</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-mono text-coral mb-4">// iterative</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Your first landing page won't be perfect. Neither was your first commit. The developers who win are the ones who ship, measure, learn, and iterate. Perfectionism is the enemy of revenue.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Belief 4 -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all duration-300 section-animate">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">"No sleazy tactics"</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-mono text-coral mb-4">// ethical</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Good DRM is about clearly communicating real value to the right people. If your product genuinely helps someone, marketing is a service — not a scam. We don't teach dark patterns, fake urgency, or manipulation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ============ WHAT WE OFFER SECTION ============ -->
  <section class="relative px-4 py-24 sm:py-32 bg-navy-light/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 section-animate">
        <p class="text-sm font-mono text-coral uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">// resources</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
          Everything Is Free
