          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Step-by-step tactical guides for specific marketing challenges.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Resource 3 -->
        <a href="/blog" class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 section-animate">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 20h9" /><path d="M16.376 3.622a1 1 0 0 1 3.002 3.002L7.368 18.635a2 2 0 0 1-.855.506l-2.872.838a.5.5 0 0 1-.62-.62l.838-2.872a2 2 0 0 1 .506-.854z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-1 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">Blog</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Tactical articles on copywriting, landing pages, email, and more.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Resource 4 -->
        <a href="/newsletter" class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 section-animate">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2" /><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-1 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">Weekly Newsletter</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">One DRM tactic every week, delivered to your inbox.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Resource 5 -->
        <a href="/tools" class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 section-animate">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-1 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">Tools & Stack</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Curated marketing tools reviewed for developers.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Resource 6 -->
        <a href="/newsletter" class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 section-animate">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-coral" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4" /><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10" /><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-1 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">DRM Cheatsheet</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Free download when you subscribe to the newsletter.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ============ CONNECT SECTION ============ -->
  <section class="relative px-4 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 section-animate">
        <p class="text-sm font-mono text-coral uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">// connect</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
          Get in Touch
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400">Have a question or suggestion? We read every email.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 section-animate">
        <!-- Twitter -->
        <a href="#" class="group flex flex-col items-center p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z" /></svg>
          <span class="text-white font-medium group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">Twitter / X</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Follow for daily tips</span>
        </a>

        <!-- GitHub -->
        <a href="#" class="group flex flex-col items-center p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" /></svg>
          <span class="text-white font-medium group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">GitHub</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Open source templates</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Email -->
        <a href="mailto:hello@codetocash.dev" class="group flex flex-col items-center p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06] hover:border-coral/20 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-coral transition-colors mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2" /><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-white font-medium group-hover:text-coral transition-colors">Email</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">hello@codetocash.dev</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ============ CTA SECTION ============ -->
  <section class="relative px-4 py-24 sm:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-deep-blue/30 via-navy-light to-coral/5 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy-light/60 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center section-animate">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
        Ready to learn how to<br />sell what you <span class="text-coral">build</span>?
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/drm-101"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-coral text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-coral/90 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg shadow-coral/20"
        >
          Start the Free DRM 101 Guide
        </a>
        <a
          href="/newsletter"
          class="px-8 py-4 border border-white/20 text-white text-lg font-medium rounded-lg hover:border-coral/50 hover:text-coral transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Subscribe to the Newsletter
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' }
  );

  document.querySelectorAll('.section-animate').forEach((el) => {
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>
